sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant UI as UI
  participant K as Kong
  participant A as Auth Service
  participant P as Profile Service
  participant SQL as SQL DB

  U->>UI: Signup form
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/auth/signup
  K->>A: forward
  A->>SQL: save credentials
  A->>P: POST /internal/users
  P->>SQL: insert user row
  P-->>A: 201
  A-->>K: 201
  K-->>UI: success
  UI-->>U: redirect login
